def is_bowl(obj:item):
    # Check if the object is a bowl
    symbol is_bowl=exists bowl: item : is_bowl(bowl) and bowl==obj
    return is_bowl

behavior crack_eggs(eggs:item, bowl:item):
    body:
        achieve cut(eggs) # Simulates cracking the eggs by cutting
        achieve inside(eggs, bowl) # Move the cracked eggs into the bowl

behavior beat_eggs_within_bowl(bowl:item):

        # Simulate beating the eggs in the bowl
        achieve close_char(char, bowl) # Character needs to be close to the bowl for beating eggs
        # Note: Actual beating is assumed by execution of the action sequence

        # Select an egg(s) instance

        achieve cut(eggs) # Crack the eggs
